  hermesIoSafetySaveSuccess: _('输入输出保护已保存，建议重启 Hermes Gateway 生效', 'Input/output safety limits saved. Restart Hermes Gateway to take effect.', '輸入輸出保護已儲存，建議重啟 Hermes Gateway 生效'),
